body: I am removing the dep to `third_party/{fft2d,flatbuffers,eigen3}` which we don't control fully and doesn't work well internally for now. Also, for some reason the `contrib/mpi:all_files` and `mpi_collectives:all_files` are missing. We should figure that out internally.
